刑、拘役或一萬五千元以下罰\r\n金。\r\n\r\n附  件","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TTDM/110%2c%e6%9d%b1%e7%b0%a1%2c21%2c20210408%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TTDM,110,東簡,21,20210408,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"東簡","JNO":"21","JDATE":"20210408","JTITLE":"妨害秩序等"}